item.description:
The squirrels are gathering their acorns & soon our pups will be romping around in piles of pretty colored leaves. What better time to welcome the beginning of autumn, visit with old friends and make some new ones too! Sunday September 23, 2012 from 11:00 am - 1:00pm
Pooches will have Fun with silly games like Apple "Picking", or they can Race through a Corn Maze, or even help us with a Paw Mural. We can't wait to hear what you have all been up to. See you Soon!

Special treat for dogs who come wearing Fall Colors!

Proof of Current Vaccines Required: Rabies, DHLPP, Bordatella
item.name: Fall Harvest Fun!
